sources.description:
Saltwater: The Battle Of Ramree Island - During the last months of WW2, an Allied mission to regain Ramree Island off the coast of Burma ends in horror when a group of soldiers find themselves trapped in dense swampland infested with deadly saltwater crocodiles. Inspired by actual events.
2021.  Stars: Charlie Bond, Steven Dolton, Ryan Harvey
